* [[Ameddurdu]]: ameqran deg-sen yakk deg [[tiddi]] imu yezmer ad yaweṭ ar 90 cm
* [[Anessas]]: D [[talmest|telmest]] [[timikrit]] (yetturba)
* [[Azirdyaw]] neɣ [[Azeṭṭen]]: D [[amerrew]] [[azɣaran]] n [[Anessas|unessas]]
